events.description:
Get your hands dirty with various open source software for working with drones, including DroneKit, MAVLink, and Mission Planner in this workshop at FOSSASIA 2016. Please join us in the Science Centre at 2:00 pm on Level 1 in the Eco Garden Lab. This is a 1-hour-workshop. 


Participation This workshop takes place at the FOSSASIA OpenTechSummit 2016 in the Science Centre Singapore. Tickets are available here: http://www.eventnook.com/event/fossasia/register Daily tickets cost 7 SGD. Website: http://2016.fossasia.org 


About Jiin Joo Ong: Ong Jiin Joo is the co-founder and CTO of Singapore-based drone solutions and services company, Garuda Robotics. &lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href="http://garuda.io/"&gt; Web  Twitter  LinkedIn&lt;a href="https://sg.linkedin.com/in/jiinjoo"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;
